attr.title: Astronautilus
attr.desc: Your ship has crash-landed on a stray rogue planet, and you're out of fuel ... It's up to you to delve beneath the frozen surface and find a way to get your ship back into space. Fight strange sea creatures and uncover the mysteries of the world beneath the ice!
attr.inst: Purchase the game from Steam (https://store.steampowered.com/app/1724120/ASTRONAUTILUS/). Enter the Steam Console and use the following command to download a compatible version: download_depot 1724120 1724121 6233168631671934006. Copy those downloaded files to the astronautilus/assets directory.
